node.text: Put some explosive power into your oblique training with this total #bossbitch move! (Or #badass if you’re a dude) Hook your band to the top of a door frame and make sure your back foot turns in when you twist.  I also like to hold the contraction at the end of each punch for extra burn and time under tension.  Grab your band and add this to your next #stayathome abs sesh! 🔥🔥🔥#obliques #abs #femaleabs #sixpackfemmes #sixpack #purefitnesssg #fitsg #fitgirls #fitsporation #boxingabstraining #punches #fitnessgirl #fitnesssg #underarmour #lornajane #fitnessfreak #covid19 #singaporecircuitbreaker #circuitbreakersg #attitude #aptitud #missthegym
